headline: Financial Stocks Are Falling. It’s About More Than AI — Heard on the Street
summary: On Monday, it was insurance brokers, hit by news that OpenAI was adding an app for homeowner insurance quotes.  On Tuesday, it was wealth brokers, after financial-technology firm Altruist introduced an AI tool for tax planning strategies.  The next day it was commercial real-estate brokerages.
